import { Component } from '@angular/core'; class Player { public static readonly NONE_EMAIL = "[none_email]" public static readonly NONE_HASH = "[none_hash]" public static readonly NONE_NAME = "[none_name]"; public static readonly NONE_PHONE_NUMBER = "[none_phone_number]"; public readonly id = -1; public readonly email = Player.NONE_EMAIL; public readonly passwordHash = Player.NONE_HASH; public readonly name = Player.NONE_NAME; public readonly phoneNumber = Player.NONE_PHONE_NUMBER; } @Component({ selector: 'app-players', templateUrl: './players.component.html', styleUrls: ['./players.component.css'] }) export class PlayersComponent { public players: Player[] = []; }
